name: Noisedeck Nano: Noisemaker
description: We're a pair of artists working on a creative tool called Noisedeck. We want to make it easy for anyone to make beautiful generative art.  We would like to work on Noisedeck full-time, and are thinking creatively about funding. We're releasing tiny collectible editions of Noisedeck as interactive NFTs -- support the project by collecting them all! The first release is our "Noisemaker" synth.  Try Noisedeck at noisedeck.app!  Thanks for your support. -- @rustysniper1 and @occi
